column5: Great day on the hardwater! All videos and pics were taken yesterday. <object width="425" height="350"><param name="movie" value=" Mr.Whiteys stomach contents.  Fresh fillets.
Thats a great video and nice looking fish  rob
Sweet video Iceguy, you guys caught some great fish. Looks like the fishing is picking up a bit. I got to wait till Sunday to get out, hopefully I can find some fish this time.   Jay
Awesome video and great day on the ice.  If I knew enough to catch fish like that thru the ice, I'd be out there more often!! LOL
Great video iceguy, perfect editing to go along with what sure looked like a perfect day on the ice.  Loved the dog in the life jacket
Wow, what an awesome time on the ice you guys had... And about the video... well done!   Cheers,  Jen
Just a super video, thanks.  Loved it.  Looks like great fishing for all there  Joey
awesome vid rob ..you guys slayed them ....hopefully it doesnt snow so we can head out tomorrow morn
That is one awsome video - you are muti-talented!    Don
Thanks for the vid Iceguy!!  Today was just as good out there.  Missed ya today bud. (noone to run the camera)
awesome video, that sure was one chunky laker.
Awesome fishing video man !!!!!!.  ..great catch,you guys put on a clinic out there yesterday WTG...
Well I thought George had gone to knee surgury heaven!! Good to see him back out there and about (and catching fish!)  Nice report iceguy!  Rob C
Wow that was amazing!  The fishing and the video!  Thanks for sharing.   lovetofish
